582
00:29:43,030 --> 00:29:44,540
I will gradually and slowly

583
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:46,900
make you feel the despair.

584
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:48,420
Enjoy

585
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:50,660
your final moments in life.

586
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:56,220
Have some hot congee to warm your stomach.

587
00:29:56,670 --> 00:29:58,140
Plain congee with goji berries.

588
00:30:00,140 --> 00:30:01,040
I have to admit,

589
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:03,580
