590
00:30:03,580 --> 00:30:04,750
Absolutely.

591
00:30:06,060 --> 00:30:07,140
As a chess player,

592
00:30:07,470 --> 00:30:09,990
I'm about to make the final move,

593
00:30:09,990 --> 00:30:11,940
